    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A creature attempting to move through the wall must make a Strength check (DC 25) to do so, which breaches the wall just long enough for the creature to pass through. If a Raiton technique is used targeting the wall or whose area also hits the wall, it is electrified for 1d4+1 rounds, dealing 1d4 electric damage per rank of the Raiton technique used to any creatures making direct contact with it.</p>\n\n\n\n",
